    "updated_at": "2023-12-04T12:19:48Z",
    "body": "No, none of those environment variables exist after running:\r\n\r\n`aws sso login --profile my-profile`\r\n\r\nThis may also be useful?\r\n\r\n```sh\r\n> aws --version\r\naws-cli/2.13.35 Python/3.11.6 Linux/6.6.3-arch1-1 source/x86_64.arch prompt/off\r\n```",
