    "updated_at": "2023-12-20T09:28:40Z",
    "body": "Ah, so I do occasionally do, for example, `AWS_PROFILE=my-profile aws sso login` but obviously that's scoped. The reason I don't want to include an AWS_PROFILE in my rc is I have multiple different profiles for different companies I am working work... however, you have just introduced me to direnv which is a solution to a problem I have always wanted to solve so thanks! And I can confirm this seems to work as expected now.",
